data.description: Your Dream Home Awaits! This charming single-story home offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and modern convenience. With 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a newly renovated kitchen, it's a haven for those seeking both space and elegance. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the bright and open floor plan, with an abundance of natural light illuminating every corner. The heart of this home is the newly renovated kitchen, a chef's dream come true. The spacious living area provides a cozy retreat for relaxation, while the adjacent dining area is perfect for family gatherings and entertaining friends. Retreat to the generous master suite with its private bath, offering a serene oasis to unwind after a long day. Three additional bedrooms provide plenty of space for family, guests, or even a home office. One of the standout features of this property is the beautiful yard adorned with mature trees. Imagine enjoying your morning coffee on the patio while taking in the natural beauty that surrounds you. The possibilities for outdoor activities and landscaping are endless. Located in a desirable neighborhood, 1106 Blewett Drive is just moments away from parks, schools, shopping, and dining options. Schedule a showing today and experience the true meaning of Texas living.
